Description:
WARNING : Evolved ARP , in the 2G/3G QOS profiles, is not applicable on this case ! Don't take into account the value :
Evolved ARP =1

In our GGSN GTPv0 is supported only if the PDP is initiated in GTPv0 (Create PDP Context). We do not support Update PDP
Context performed in GTPv0 if the PDP was previously initiated in GTPv1.
